name: Synapcrosis
description:
As we found ourselves grappling with this whole Schrödinger's cat situation, of whether we are actually alive versus are we living in a simulation. So, here is my depiction of how concious stream of thoughts that comes and goes constantly in our head that may leave us stuck in between states of awake and asleep, of being alive and undead. Hopefully one day we will get to decide to pay no mind to all these distractions and abstractions and just finally.. live !

Created by Izealist in 2022 as a submission to Billelis' competition (3D model made by him, this is minted with his permission)
